# Gemini Comment Bot – Web Extension

This browser extension lets you generate high-quality comments using Google's Gemini API directly from your browser popup.

## 🔧 How to Use

1. Load the extension:
   - Visit `chrome://extensions/`
   - Enable Developer Mode
   - Click “Load unpacked” → select this folder

2. Enter your Gemini API key (from https://makersuite.google.com/)
3. Paste post text → choose tone → hit Generate.
4. Copy the result or paste it manually into X, LinkedIn, etc.

## 🧠 Features

- Gemini API integration
- Local API key storage
- Copy-to-clipboard support
- Tiny, fast, and private

